text: So different versions of the pac which have different R version dependencies is valid I think. This is how R knows whether what version of the package to grab based on the R version you’re using. The only thing that looks possibly buggish to me there is that the Matrix version are the same, but I suspect thats still allowable due to a) the fact that they’re base packages, and b) the R version dependencies are still different.
